    <!--git-->
    <h2>Git LifeCycle</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>File Statuses Untracked/Tracked = use add fileName to Tracked = unmodified</li>
        <li>File Statuses Unmodified/Modified = if file change after add</li>
        <li>File Statuses Modified/staged = add again after change</li>
        <li>File Statuses staged/Unmodified = commit to Unmodified the staged file</li>
        <li>read pdf = end</li>
    </ol>

    <!--git-->
    <h2>Git Branch</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>git clear = to clear commendline</li>
        <li>git branch = show branch</li>
        <li>git branch develop = new branch name 'develop'</li>
        <li>git checkout develop = switched to branch 'develop'</li>
        <li>notic: if you switched in develop branch files saves just in that</li>
        <li>git branch -d develop = delete develop branch</li>
        <li>git  merge develop = checkout master branch and merge develop branch to save on master(save comment in vim)</li>
    </ol>

